                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17030707-2-defend3 t17030707-2-deflabel9"></join>, called the Butcher of Gloucester, of the Parish of <placeName id="t17030707-2-defloc10">St. Martins in the Fields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17030707-2-defloc10" type="placeName" value="St. Martins in the Fields"></interp>
