                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17030707-2-defend3 t17030707-2-defloc10"></join>, was indicted for the <rs id="t17030707-2-off11" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17030707-2-off11" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
